01:52:58.040 --> 01:53:00.040
So who brought the plates?

01:53:00.040 --> 01:53:02.040
Oh, you were supposed to bring them.

01:53:02.040 --> 01:53:04.040
Yeah.

01:53:04.040 --> 01:53:06.040
I'm so proud of you.

01:53:06.040 --> 01:53:08.040
I'm so proud of you, too.

01:53:08.040 --> 01:54:17.300
I'm so proud of you, too.

01:54:17.300 --> 01:54:19.300
All those people looking at us.

01:54:19.300 --> 01:54:21.300
I feel like goldfish.

